title: Ashish Chakrapani
text: Ashish Chakrapani is an English <a href="cricket">cricket</a>er. He made his <a href="List%20A%20cricket">List A</a> debut on 22 July 2021, for <a href="Warwickshire%20County%20Cricket%20Club">Warwickshire</a> in the <a href="2021%20Royal%20London%20One-Day%20Cup">2021 Royal London One-Day Cup</a>.
